1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper focuses on backscatter communication, which is a subfield of networking and internet architecture. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) - The paper proposes the integration of unmanned ground vehicles (UGVs) into the backscatter system, which falls under the field of robotics. 
3. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper discusses the optimization of energy consumption in communication, which is a topic related to information theory. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper proposes a joint graph mobility and backscatter communication model, which involves control and optimization of a system. 
5. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) - The paper involves the coordination of multiple agents (UGVs and IoT devices) in a system, which is a topic related to multiagent systems.
